V0407_01_00_00_0.text: You'll learn firsthand what unstoppable power feels like!

V0407_01_00_01_0.text: Witness the strength of my Galaxy-Eyes!

V0407_01_00_04_0.text:
Yuma! Astral!
I'll take you both on!

V0407_01_00_05_0.text:
I can tell you've improved your skills, Yuma.
But how much?

V0407_01_00_06_0.text: You're the only foe that's worthy of crushing, Astral!

V0407_01_00_07_1.text: You taught me everything YOU know, but I know more!

V0407_01_00_08_0.text: I'll hunt your Number, along with your soul!

V0407_01_00_09_1.text: That is why I will hunt you down!

V0407_01_00_10_0.text: Every living thing will someday come to an end.

V0407_01_00_10_1.text: But I'll make sure Barian World goes down first!

V0407_01_00_11_0.text:
There can be only one Galaxy-Eyes master.
And that's me!

V0407_03_00_01_0.text: There's nothing left you can do!

V0407_03_00_04_0.text: Your strategies aren't bad, but they're not as good as mine!

V0407_05_00_00_0.text:
This isn't luck!
A true Duelist can draw the card he needs!

V0407_07_09_00_0.text: I flip over my Set card!

V0407_08_00_00_0.text: I activate the Spell Card, Accellight!

V0407_08_00_00_1.text: It Summons a Level 4 or lower Photon or Galaxy monster!

V0407_08_00_01_0.text: I activate the Quick-Play Spell, Xyz Double Back!

V0407_08_00_02_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
Overlay Regen!

V0407_08_00_03_0.text:
I activate my Quick-Play Spell!
Galaxy Storm!

V0407_08_00_03_1.text: I destroy an Xyz Monster that has no Overlay Units!

V0407_08_00_04_0.text: I activate the Quick-Play Spell, Hyper Galaxy!

V0407_08_00_05_0.text: I activate the Spell Card, Photon Sanctuary!

V0407_08_00_06_1.text: I activate the Spell Card, Photon Hand!

V0407_08_00_07_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
Photon Booster!

V0407_08_00_08_0.text: I activate my Spell Card, Photon Veil!

V0407_08_00_09_0.text: I activate the Quick-Play Spell, Photon Lead!

V0407_08_00_09_1.text: I Special Summon a Level 4 or lower LIGHT monster!

V0407_08_00_10_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
Galaxy Expedition!

V0407_08_00_10_1.text: It Special Summons a Photon or Galaxy monster from my deck!

V0407_08_00_11_0.text: I activate the Equip Spell, Galaxy Zero!

V0407_08_00_12_0.text: When this card's gone, the equipped monster's ATK dip to 0!

V0407_08_00_13_0.text: I activate the Ritual Spell, Luminous Dragon Ritual!

V0407_08_00_14_0.text: I activate my Spell Card, Monster Reborn!

V0407_08_00_15_0.text: I activate the Spell Card, Book of Moon!

V0407_08_00_15_1.text: It switches a face-up monster to face-down Defense Position!

V0407_08_00_16_0.text:
This will decide my fate!
I activate Message in a Bottle!

V0407_08_00_16_1.text: I revive 3 monsters with different Levels from my Graveyard!

V0407_08_00_17_0.text: I activate the Spell Card, Polymerization!

V0407_08_00_18_0.text: I pay my LP to activate the Spell Card, Galaxy Trance!

V0407_08_00_19_0.text: I banish one card in play to activate my Quick-Play Spell!

V0407_08_00_20_0.text: I activate the Quick-Play Spell, Photon Trident!

V0407_08_00_21_0.text: Since you took damage, Photon Trident nukes a Spell or Trap!

V0407_08_00_22_0.text: I activate the Continuous Trap, Galaxy Wave!

V0407_08_00_22_1.text: Every time I Xyz Summon, this card deals you damage!

V0407_08_00_23_0.text:
Galaxy Wave's effect activates!
Take this damage!

V0407_08_00_25_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Eternal Bond!

V0407_08_00_25_1.text: It resurrects Photon monsters by negating their effects!

V0407_08_00_26_0.text: I banish Eternal Bond from my Graveyard to use its effect!

V0407_08_00_26_1.text: I gain control of one Photon monster!

V0407_08_00_27_0.text:
I activate my Continuous Trap!
Photon Change!

V0407_08_00_28_0.text: I send a monster to the Graveyard to activate Photon Change!

V0407_08_00_30_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Double Dragon Descent!

V0407_08_00_30_1.text: Your attack switches to the Dragon that I Special Summon!

V0407_08_00_31_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Photon Current!

V0407_08_00_32_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Eternal Galaxy!

V0407_08_00_33_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Cipher Spectrum!

V0407_08_00_34_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Cipher Bit!

V0407_08_00_35_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Double Cipher!

V0407_09_00_00_1.text: When Galaxy-Eyes battles, I banish both our monsters!

V0407_09_00_01_0.text: Neo Galaxy-Eyes negates the effects of all other cards!

V0407_09_00_02_1.text: It uses 1 Overlay Unit to absorb all your Overlay Units!

V0407_09_00_02_2.text: That raises its ATK and the number of times it can attack!

V0407_09_00_03_0.text: When Galaxy-Eyes is on my field, I can Special Summon this!

V0407_09_00_04_0.text: Afterglow Dragon's no longer an Overlay Unit, so watch this!

V0407_09_00_06_0.text: I play Galaxy-Eyes Cloudragon's effect from my Graveyard!

V0407_09_00_07_0.text: I activate Galaxy-Eyes Full Armor Photon Dragon's effect!

V0407_09_00_07_1.text: It changes its Equip Cards into Overlay Units!

V0407_09_00_08_0.text: Photon Dragon uses an Overlay Unit to get rid of a card!

V0407_09_00_09_0.text: If Dyson Sphere has an Overlay Unit, it can stop an attack.

V0407_09_00_10_1.text: Two monsters in my Graveyard become its Overlay Units!

V0407_09_00_11_0.text: Dyson Sphere uses an Overlay Unit to activate its effect!

V0407_09_00_11_1.text: It can now attack you directly this turn!

V0407_09_00_12_0.text: Illumiknight uses an Overlay Unit to activate its effect!

V0407_09_00_13_0.text: Embodiment of Crime uses 1 Overlay Unit to wield its effect!

V0407_09_00_13_1.text: It forces all your monsters to attack it!

V0407_09_00_14_1.text: For just 1 Overlay Unit, all my face-up monsters gain ATK!

V0407_09_00_15_0.text: During my Standby Phase, Acid Golem loves to make me suffer.

V0407_09_00_16_0.text: When a Spell activates, Titanic Galaxy can use its effect!

V0407_09_00_17_1.text: It uses 1 Overlay Unit to redirect your attack!

V0407_09_00_19_0.text: Since I have no other monsters, Dragluon's effect activates!

V0407_09_00_21_0.text: I use 1 Overlay Unit to play Prime Photon Dragon's effect!

V0407_09_00_21_1.text: It gains ATK for every Rank that's currently in play!

V0407_09_00_22_0.text: Prime Photon Dragon controls the future!

V0407_09_00_22_1.text: So it returns to play on my second turn!

V0407_09_00_23_0.text: Galaxy-Eyes Photon Lord uses an Overlay Unit!

V0407_09_00_24_0.text: Galaxy-Eyes Photon Lord activates its effect!

V0407_09_00_25_0.text: If Dark Matter Dragon is Xyz Summoned, its effect activates!

V0407_09_00_26_0.text: I use one of Dark Matter Dragon's Overlay Units!

V0407_09_00_26_1.text: It can now attack twice this turn!

V0407_09_00_27_0.text: Paladynamo uses 2 Overlay Units to activate its effect!

V0407_09_00_28_0.text: When Paladynamo is destroyed, I draw a card!

V0407_09_00_29_0.text: I can use Galaxion's Overlay Units to energize its effects!

V0407_09_00_30_0.text: My Blast Dragon's effect activates when it's Xyz Summoned!

V0407_09_00_31_0.text: Photon Blast Dragon uses 1 Overlay Unit to power its effect!

V0407_09_00_32_0.text: When Overlay Sentinel is Summoned, it switches to Defense!

V0407_09_00_33_0.text: I banish Overlay Sentinel from the Grave to use its effect!

V0407_09_00_34_0.text: I banish Overlay Booster from the Grave to play its effect!

V0407_09_00_35_0.text: You know what to do, Orbital 7!

V0407_09_00_37_0.text: I tribute Orbital 7 to activate its effect!

V0407_09_00_39_0.text:
Orbital!
Sacrifice yourself for me and Hart!

V0407_09_00_40_0.text:
Your friend's calling you, Orbital.
So come on out!

V0407_09_00_41_0.text: Lillybot, you're a million times more useful than Orbital 7.

V0407_09_00_42_0.text: When I Summon Galaxy Worm, I can activate its effect!

V0407_09_00_43_0.text: I send Kuriphoton to the Graveyard to activate its effect!

V0407_09_00_44_0.text: Kuriphoton's effect activates from my Graveyard!

V0407_09_00_45_1.text: It splits apart into the monsters that I fused together.

V0407_09_00_46_0.text: I activate Dimension Wanderer's effect from my hand!

V0407_09_00_47_0.text: When I Special Summon this card, I can Summon another copy!

V0407_09_00_48_0.text: Get these Numbers out of my sight!

V0407_09_00_49_0.text: When I Summon this card, I can Special Summon another one!

V0407_09_00_52_0.text: I banish a Photon from my Grave to use my Pirate's effect!

V0407_09_00_54_0.text:
Photon Leo activates its effect!
Howling Blow!

V0407_09_00_54_1.text: Now you have to start your strategy all over again.

V0407_09_00_55_0.text: When I Summon Photon Wyvern, your Set cards are destroyed!

V0407_09_00_56_0.text: When Photon Sabre Tiger is Summoned, it can use its effect!

V0407_09_00_57_0.text: Photon Vanisher lets me acquire Galaxy-Eyes Photon Dragon!

V0407_09_00_58_0.text: Reverse Buster destroys your face-down monster!

V0407_09_00_60_0.text: I Tribute Galaxy Wizard to activate its effect!

V0407_09_00_61_0.text: I didn't Tribute Summon my Knight, so its effect activates!

V0407_09_00_62_0.text: I activate Galaxy Tyranno's effect from my hand!

V0407_09_00_63_0.text: If Tyranno Special Summons itself, another effect activates!

V0407_09_00_63_1.text: It can Xyz Summon a Galaxy Xyz Monster!

V0407_09_00_64_0.text: Galaxy Mirror Sage's Flip Effect activates!

V0407_09_00_65_0.text: When Galaxy Mirror Sage is destroyed, its effect activates!

V0407_09_00_66_0.text: I activate Paladin of Photon Dragon's effect!

V0407_09_00_66_1.text: I Tribute this card to Special Summon Galaxy-Eyes!

V0407_09_00_67_0.text: When my Paladin destroys a monster in battle, I draw a card!

V0407_09_00_68_0.text: I activate Galaxy Cleric's effect from my hand!

V0407_09_00_70_0.text: By showing you a Photon monster, I can Special Summon this!

V0407_09_00_71_0.text: Brave's ATK and DEF become the same as the monster I choose!

V0407_09_00_72_0.text: I send a LIGHT monster to the Graveyard to Summon this card!

V0407_09_00_73_0.text: By Special Summoning Galaxy Soldier, its effect activates!

V0407_09_00_74_0.text: I use 1 Overlay Unit to activate Cipher Dragon's effect!

V0407_09_00_75_0.text: Neo Galaxy-Eyes Cipher Dragon's effect activates!

V0407_09_00_76_0.text: I use 1 Overlay Unit to play Cipher Blade Dragon's effect!

V0407_09_00_77_0.text: When Cipher Blade Dragon is destroyed, its effect activates!

V0407_09_00_79_0.text: Cipher Etranger activates its effect from my Graveyard!

V0407_09_00_81_0.text: Cipher Mirror Knight's effect activates from my hand!

V0407_09_00_82_0.text: Since my Knight went to the Graveyard, its effect activates!

V0407_09_00_83_0.text: I discard a card to activate Cipher Twin Raptor's effect!

V0407_11_01_00_0.text: I Summon my monster in Defense Position.

V0407_11_08_01_0.text:
I build the Overlay Network!
I Xyz Summon!

V0407_37_00_00_0.text: From the darkness of the universe comes a ray of hope!

V0407_37_00_00_1.text: The true embodiment of the light!

V0407_13_00_00_0.text: Say hello to Galaxy-Eyes Photon Dragon!

V0407_37_00_01_0.text: The universe coalesces into the light of chaos!

V0407_37_00_02_0.text: The radiance of the solar system guides me to a new world!

V0407_13_00_04_0.text: The new embodiment of pure light!

V0407_37_00_03_0.text: I will crush any hope for your future!

V0407_13_00_07_0.text: Feast your eyes on Number 13: Embodiment of Crime!

V0407_37_00_04_0.text: Number 30 is here to melt everything out of existence!

V0407_37_00_05_0.text: The myriad of hopes in my mind merge into one!

V0407_13_00_10_0.text: Witness Number 38: Hope Harbinger Dragon Titanic Galaxy!

V0407_37_00_06_0.text: The golden dragon manifests from thunder and lightning!

V0407_37_00_07_0.text:
Show yourself!
Number 62: Galaxy-Eyes Prime Photon Dragon!

V0407_37_00_07_1.text: Unite the dragons that live between light and dark!

V0407_13_00_13_0.text:
This is the Number I wield!
Galaxy-Eyes Prime Photon Dragon!

V0407_37_00_08_0.text: When the universe ends, this ruler rises!

V0407_13_00_15_0.text:
Go!
Number 95: Galaxy-Eyes Dark Matter Dragon!

V0407_13_00_30_0.text: Numeral Hunter will illuminate the shadows in your soul!

V0407_13_00_46_0.text: I'll render your face-down cards useless.

V0407_13_00_50_0.text:
Come on out!
Galaxy Mirror Sage!

V0407_13_00_51_0.text:
Paladin of Photon Dragon!
Soar to the sky!

V0407_37_00_10_0.text: The light in the darkness shines the path to the future!

V0407_13_00_56_0.text:
Make yourself known!
Rank 9 Neo Galaxy-Eyes Cipher Dragon!

V0407_13_00_57_0.text:
Come on out!
Rank 9 Galaxy-Eyes Cipher Blade Dragon!

V0407_19_00_00_0.text:
Galaxy-Eyes Photon Dragon!
Let 'em have it!

V0407_19_00_04_0.text: Galaxy-Eyes Full Armor Photon Dragon attacks!

V0407_19_00_05_0.text: Dyson Sphere rains down the destruction!

V0407_19_00_09_0.text: Acid Golem's strength is beyond your imagining!

V0407_19_00_10_0.text: Go, Hope Harbinger Dragon Titanic Galaxy!

V0407_19_00_11_0.text: Take the full brunt of Dragluon's power!

V0407_19_00_15_0.text:
Take this!
Galaxy-Eyes Dark Matter Dragon attacks!

V0407_19_00_46_0.text: When this card attacks, you can't activate Spells or Traps!

V0407_21_00_01_1.text:
Get on with it!
It's your turn!

V0407_21_00_05_0.text: You're a little tougher than I expected.

V0407_28_00_00_0.text: You need more heart if you want to defeat me.

V0407_28_00_01_0.text: Never forget the name of the hunter who defeated you!

V0407_28_00_02_0.text: You have good Dueling skills, but you'll never beat me.

V0407_28_00_03_0.text: Whatever strategies you try, they'll all fail against me.

V0407_28_00_04_0.text: I'm not the type who'd lose to an amateur like you, Yuma.

V0407_28_00_05_0.text: If you keep coming back, I'll keep defeating you.

V0407_28_00_06_0.text: I know all your strategies, Astral.

V0407_28_00_08_0.text:
I always hoped to reach your level.
And I finally have.

V0407_28_00_09_0.text: Today's the day that the student overcame his master.

V0407_28_00_11_0.text: A single card known as Galaxy-Eyes brought me this far.

V0407_29_00_00_0.text: I won't let this be my final Duel...

V0407_29_00_01_0.text:
I won't give up.
Not until I crush you!

V0407_29_00_02_0.text:
I've never encountered a strategy that tough.
Well done.

V0407_29_00_03_0.text: You have the victory for now, but I'll come to take it back.

V0407_29_00_04_0.text: Yuma, you never cease to amaze me.

V0407_29_00_04_1.text: No matter how many times you fall, you always get back up.

V0407_29_00_06_0.text:
Quinton, I mean Christopher...
I will defeat you someday.

V0407_29_00_08_0.text: As long as you have a Number, I will hunt you down!

V0407_29_00_09_0.text: If we ever meet again, Mizar...

V0407_29_00_09_1.text: Maybe you can tell me why you're acting like this...

V0407_29_00_10_0.text: Go and do what you think is right, Mizar.

V0407_30_00_02_0.text:
Me make a mistake?
In your dreams.

V0407_34_00_00_0.text:
I'm disappointed.
All you do is defend.

V0407_34_00_01_0.text: I know what you'll play next!

V0407_34_00_03_0.text: The fire in my soul will boil the poison out of me!

V0407_34_00_06_0.text: The only one you can count on is yourself!

V0407_34_00_07_0.text: I've never seen anything like this!

V0407_35_00_00_0.text: I'm known as the Number Hunter.

V0407_36_00_00_0.text: The rest of the Duel is in your hands.

V0407_36_00_02_0.text: How could I play this badly!

V0407_36_00_10_0.text: You better not be the reason why we lose, Christopher.
